sentences.english: The zero-offset (z0) section is an important achievement in seismic reflection imaging.

sentences.english: CTD Profiling System is the principal instrument for acquiring hydrographic data in situ.

sentences.english: The application of K section method in Huanglashi landslide is mainly introduced in this paper.
sentences.chinese: 介绍了K剖面法在黄腊石滑坡中的应用情况。

sentences.english: One of the characteristics of lava and debris valleys is a U-shaped transverse profile.

sentences.english: In addition to cutaways, we also explain physics.

sentences.english: This illustration shows a vertical section through the locust.

sentences.english: The evidence of human activities around Jiangling area was revealed by sporopollen records from sediments in the Jiangling section, Hubei Province.

sentences.english: The profile distribution of different fractions of organic carbon were not altered by intensive practice.

sentences.english: Thus it may be for reference in prediction of added-mass of other profiles.
sentences.chinese: 从而为预估其它剖面附加质量提供参考。
